      <title>香港法官裁定 Segantii 案将移交至地方法院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/segantii-case-will-move-to-district-court-hong-kong-judge-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Segantii Capital Management 的内幕交易案将移交至地方法院，地方法院可判处最高七年的监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/segantii-case-will-move-to-district-court-hong-kong-judge-rules</guid>
