      <title>汇丰增持中国基金股份 合资公司将成为多数股东</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/hsbc-to-boost-stake-in-china-fund-jv-to-become-majority-owner</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司同意收购其合作伙伴在中国基金合资企业中的部分股份，成为大股东，并助力其在中国这个世界第二大经济体的扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/hsbc-to-boost-stake-in-china-fund-jv-to-become-majority-owner</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 02:18:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
